data.description: Spacious move-in ready home with a 3-Car Garage. Welcome to this stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom single-family home that boasts an open floor plan and high ceilings. The primary bedroom features beautiful wood laminate flooring, and the living room is spacious with vaulted ceilings, and an abundance of natural light. The kitchen is equipped with stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops and plenty of room for family gatherings. The bathroom is elegantly designed with granite countertops and double sinks. The exterior features a beautiful front yard with excellent curb appeal. The home is a quick drive to restaurants, shopping centers, grocery stores, the local gym, and it also offers quick freeway access. The second living room, can be turned into a 4th bedroom. Come take a look before its gone!
